            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Hic sita sum matrona genus nomen<lb break="no" n="2"/>que Veturia Fortunati coniux de patre Vetu<lb break="no" n="3"/>rio nata ter novenos misera et nupta bis octo <lb n="4"/>per annos unicuba uniiuga quae post <lb n="5"/>sex partus uno superstite obii <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> Iulius Fortunatus |(centurio) <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> II <expan><abbr>ad</abbr><ex>iutricis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>coniugi incomparabili et insigni in se pietate
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Inschriftträger: (TitAq) Arca mit zugehörigem Deckel.</p>
            </div>
